        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="{{ asset('images/image.png') }}" alt="Boxing" class="card-header-img">
        <div class="card-header">
            Boxing
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
            <p>Learn boxing techniques and improve your overall fitness and coordination.</p>
            <a href="{{ path('boxing') }}" class="button">Read More</a>
